flowchart TD
    Start([Start: loop-detector.js]) --> RegisterHandlers["Register Global Error Handlers"]
    RegisterHandlers --> UncaughtHandler["process.on('uncaughtException')<br/>Currently: exit(1)"]
    UncaughtHandler --> UnhandledHandler["process.on('unhandledRejection')<br/>Currently: exit(1)"]
    UnhandledHandler --> Timeout["Set timeout: 3 seconds<br/>(Fail-closed)<br/>Currently: exit(2)"]

    Timeout --> StdinInit["Initialize stdin<br/>Set encoding to utf8"]
    StdinInit --> StdinListen["Listen for stdin events"]

    StdinListen --> DataEvent{"Data event?"}
    DataEvent -->|Yes| ReadData["Accumulate input data"]
    ReadData --> StdinListen
    DataEvent -->|No| ErrorEvent{"Error event?"}

    ErrorEvent -->|Yes| HandleStdinError["Clear timeout<br/>Exit(0)"]
    ErrorEvent -->|No| EndEvent{"End event?"}

    EndEvent -->|Yes| TimeoutCheck{"Timeout expired?"}
    TimeoutCheck -->|Yes| TimeoutExit["Clear timeout<br/>Exit(2)<br/>Security fail-closed"]
    TimeoutCheck -->|No| ParseJSON["Parse JSON from input data"]

    ParseJSON --> JSONValid{"Valid JSON?"}
    JSONValid -->|No| InvalidJSON["Exit(0)<br/>Permit - no input"]
    JSONValid -->|Yes| ValidateInput["Validate input structure<br/>Check: tool_name, tool_input, file_path"]

    ValidateInput --> InputValid{"Valid input?"}
    InputValid -->|No| PermitNoInput["Exit(0)<br/>Permit - no input"]
    InputValid -->|Yes| CheckTool{"Tool is Edit or Write?"}

    CheckTool -->|No| PermitOther["Exit(0)<br/>Permit - non-restricted tool"]
    CheckTool -->|Yes| CheckPath{"FilePath exists?"}

    CheckPath -->|No| PermitNoPath["Exit(0)<br/>Permit - no file path"]
    CheckPath -->|Yes| RunDetection["Execute: checkLoop(filePath)"]

    RunDetection --> LoadState["Load state file<br/>loop-detector-state.json"]
    LoadState --> NormalizeFile["Normalize file path:<br/>lowercase + slash unification"]
    NormalizeFile --> ProcessTimestamps["Filter old timestamps<br/>Remove > 5min old entries"]
    ProcessTimestamps --> AppendTimestamp["Append current timestamp"]

    AppendTimestamp --> CheckThreshold{"Edit count >= Threshold?"}
    CheckThreshold -->|No| SaveState["Save updated state"]
    SaveState --> PermitContinue["Exit(0)<br/>Permit - allow edit"]

    CheckThreshold -->|Yes| CheckSuppression{"Warning suppression<br/>active?"}
    CheckSuppression -->|Yes| UpdateSuppression["Update suppression state<br/>Skip warning"]
    UpdateSuppression --> SaveState

    CheckSuppression -->|No| DisplayWarning["Display warning message<br/>with analysis hints"]
    DisplayWarning --> LogWarning["Log warning to:<br/>loop-detection-log.json"]
    LogWarning --> RecordTimestamp["Record warning timestamp<br/>for suppression"]
    RecordTimestamp --> SaveStateBlock["Save updated state"]
    SaveStateBlock --> BlockEdit["Exit(2)<br/>BLOCK - infinite loop detected<br/>UNIFIED exit code"]

    HandleStdinError --> End([End])
    InvalidJSON --> End
    PermitNoInput --> End
    PermitOther --> End
    PermitNoPath --> End
    PermitContinue --> End
    BlockEdit --> End
    TimeoutExit --> End

    style Start fill:#e1f5e1
    style End fill:#ffe1e1
    style BlockEdit fill:#ffcccc,stroke:#cc0000,stroke-width:3px
    style TimeoutExit fill:#ffcccc,stroke:#cc0000,stroke-width:3px
    style UncaughtHandler fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ff6600,stroke-width:2px
    style UnhandledHandler fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ff6600,stroke-width:2px
    style Timeout fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ff6600,stroke-width:2px

    Note["NOTE: Modification target<br/>─────────────────<br/>1. uncaughtException: exit(1) → exit(2)<br/>2. unhandledRejection: exit(1) → exit(2)<br/>Ensures consistent error handling<br/>exit code 2 = hook validation failure"]
    Note -.->|Reference| UncaughtHandler
    Note -.->|Reference| UnhandledHandler
